      "text": "The operations division concentrated on infrastructure modernization projects\nthroughout the year.\nSeveral aging systems were retired and replaced with cloud-based alternatives,\nresulting in improved scalability and reduced maintenance overhead.\nTechnical teams completed multiple migration phases ahead of schedule,\nwhile automation initiatives decreased manual processing requirements across\nseveral business functions.\nPerformance metrics indicated measurable gains in system availability,\ntransaction throughput, and incident response times.\nFuture efforts will focus on optimizing resource utilization\nand completing the remaining integration milestones.",
      "fontSize": 8.288888888888893,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The operations division concentrated on infrastructure modernization projects throughout the year.\nSeveral aging systems were retired and replaced with cloud-based alternatives,\nresulting in improved scalability and reduced maintenance overhead.\nTechnical teams completed multiple migration phases ahead of schedule,\nwhile automation initiatives decreased manual processing requirements across several business functions.\nPerformance metrics indicated measurable gains in system availability,\ntransaction throughput, and incident response times.\nFuture efforts will focus on optimizing resource utilization\nand completing the remaining integration milestones.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DWhbEglbwyUMljn9eyi0L",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1087.5952323404947,
      "y": 1192.0138888888887,
      "width": 330.8095353190107,
      "height": 113.97222222222227,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#099268",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 551322013,
      "version": 697,
      "versionNonce": 608906045,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "bf5Cul90E1tO08jobGCSz",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1780194115907,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The customer insights group dedicated the year to market research,\nstakeholder interviews, and behavioral analysis.\nSurveys were conducted across multiple regions to evaluate consumer preferences\nand purchasing patterns.\nThe resulting data suggested growing demand for simplified workflows,\nenhanced training resources, and improved support responsiveness.\nResearchers also identified several emerging market segments\nthat may present future growth opportunities.\nRecommendations emphasized customer experience initiatives,\ntargeted outreach strategies, and continued monitoring of changing industry\ntrends.",
      "fontSize": 8.288888888888893,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The customer insights group dedicated the year to market research,\nstakeholder interviews, and behavioral analysis.\nSurveys were conducted across multiple regions to evaluate consumer preferences\nand purchasing patterns.\nThe resulting data suggested growing demand for simplified workflows,\nenhanced training resources, and improved support responsiveness.\nResearchers also identified several emerging market segments\nthat may present future growth opportunities.\nRecommendations emphasized customer experience initiatives,\ntargeted outreach strategies, and continued monitoring of changing industry trends.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
